data.description: Seller is offering  up to $2500 for buyers closing costs with an expectable offer!!!  Prepare to be captivated! Nestled in the prestigious Tranquil Hill Plantation within Dorchester School District 2. Welcome to the refined elegance of 9177 Parlor Drive. This spacious 2600+ sq foot exquisite three-story end unit is complete with a two-car garage and fully screened-in balconies on each floor. Special features adorn this residence, starting with the first floor's versatile bonus room and half bath - perfect for an office, home gym, guest room, or playroom. The second floor's open floor plan creates an inviting space for entertaining, with a kitchen boasting 42' two-toned cabinets, beautiful quartz countertops, and sleek modern appliances. .Indulge in the splendor of a beautiful dining room and  living rooms adorned with a custom fireplace. The third floor is dedicate to comfort, offering three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a laundry room. The primary suite is a sanctuary featuring an ensuite bathroom with dual vanities, a walk-in closet, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Begin your day with a moment of quiet reflection on the third-floor balcony of the primary suite.   Tranquil Hill Plantation elevates your living experience with lavish community amenities, including a pool and a dog park. Nestled conveniently close to shopping, restaurants, medical centers, and interstates, this neighborhood is but a brief drive to the Air Force Base and Boeing. Welcome to a community that seamlessly weaves together comfort, convenience, and an extravagant touch of luxury! Noteworthy, the HOA covers insurance, roof landscaping, pool, termite bond, and exterior building maintenance, and the homes receive a power wash every other year.  Additional upgrades.  * luxury vinyl floors  * New Countertops. * All appliances will convey, including washer and dryer * All 3 floors of the balcony are screened-in * A new fence * New grass installed November 2023 * 2023. Keyless entry door and the garage opener * Front driveway was extended * Shelves in the garage were added. * Home can be purchased fully furnished at additional cost.
